commit.message:
no string conversion when the parameter of the method of the plugin is
Object.

introduce BeforeInvocation and AfterInvocation annotation to capture
method call and __listMethods__ method to let js can query supported
method of plugins.
add methods for int, double and boolean type.

Merge pull request #2 from takawitter/imp-add-robodovalib

add sources of libRobodova
add runInBackground method to CDVCommandDelegate and its Impl.
move to new style binding notations.
add license terms to each source file.
Minimum Cordova bindings and sample app.

issue_comments.body:
Hi jeremykei.
I will push the sources in few days :)

I added source files.
You can open project at robodova / platforms / ios / RobodovaLib by Xcode.
And please try these commands to get universal (for both simulator and device) binary.

``` bash
xcodebuild -sdk iphoneos7.1 -arch armv7 -arch armv7s
xcodebuild -sdk iphonesimulator -arch i386
xcrun lipo -create build/Release-iphonesimulator/libRobodova.a build/Release-iphoneos/libRobodova.a -output ../robovm/RobodovaSampleApp/libs/libRobodova.a 
```
